  m_text: "OBJECTIVE\nCapture all 4 Enemy Flags and bring them to your Side!\n\nCONTROLS\nLeft
    Click  = Select an Agent on your Team\nWASD / Arrows  = Move Selected Agent\n\nRULES\n\u2022
    Can only carry one Flag at a time\n\u2022 Score by going back to your own Flag
    Zone\n\u2022 Getting tagged in Enemy Territory = sent to prison\n\u2022 Walk
    into the Enemy Prison to free a Teammate"
